to be none,

01:05:48.403 --> 01:05:52.906
even while intoxicating
ourselves with it all.

01:05:52.907 --> 01:05:57.286
And yet, how do we
still seek purpose?

01:05:57.287 --> 01:06:01.915
And where do we hope
to find it if we're so busy

01:06:01.916 --> 01:06:05.085
